BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:HIwpaJ-Wge8rAv2mgjcZC
SUMMARY:Moments with a Mentor
DTSTAMP:20260320T165341Z
DTSTART:20260320T160000Z
DESCRIPTION:Moments with a Mentor Moments with a Mentor is a unique network
	ing and professional development experience designed to connect emerging l
	eaders with established professionals in an intimate\, conversation-focuse
	d setting. This event creates space for meaningful dialogue\, guidance\, a
	nd inspiration as participants engage in small-group or one-on-one mentori
	ng sessions. Attendees will have the opportunity to hear personal stories\
	, gain practical career insights\, and learn strategies for navigating pro
	fessional challenges from leaders across a variety of industries. Whether 
	you're seeking direction\, building confidence\, or expanding your network
	\, Moments with a Mentor offers a supportive environment to grow and be in
	spired. Join us for an empowering experience that encourages connection\, 
	fosters mentorship\, and strengthens our community's future leaders-one co
	nversation at a time.\n\nhttps://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/mom
	ents-with-a-mentor/17665196/2026-03-20T00\n\nFrom SEAtoday - Learning & Ed
	ucation
URL:https://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/moments-with-a-mentor/176
	65196/2026-03-20T00
LOCATION:Seattle Southside Chamber of Commerce\, 3100 S 176th St Suite 210\
	, SeaTac\, WA
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:seatoday-learning
CATEGORIES:SEAtoday - Learning & Education
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT1H30M
END:VEVENT
